{"tid":2257452,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署支持英澳紐加自由行動協議 需要10萬人支持","createTime":"2020-10-25T07:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T09:35:10.000Z","uid":10540,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3fc2d8232704548deffe90f954d2b32a6991ef","tid":2257452,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/Jh2vrwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FJh2vrwq.jpg&h=e0bcee73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國脫歐大戲已經接近尾聲了，有關加英澳紐&ldquo;四國互通&rdquo; (CANZUK Freemovement)的消息又開始了新一輪的熱炒，四國互通如果真的能實現，那麼將來&ldquo;英加澳紐&rdquo;四個國家的公民無需任何簽證，就可以自由在四個國家工作，居住，或退休。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">也就是說，您只要擁有加拿大，英國，澳大利亞，紐西蘭這四個國家中任意一個身份，就相當於移民四個國家了，享受其他三國公民的同等所有權。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n四國互通包括以下幾個方面的&ldquo;共享&rdquo;：<br />\n-貿易<br />\n-國家之間公民工作，旅遊，退休居住免簽<br />\n-醫療教育共享<br />\n-自由往來<br />\n-安全協調<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">如果真的實現四國互通，&ldquo;英加澳紐&rdquo;的護照CP值將會猛增，真正實現一本護照等同於四個國籍的美好願景。有BNO的你應該都要支持！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/554372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F554372&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=e866162b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/554372</a>"},{"pid":"c5c0d5aa80b4c56cbf2aa62a39a0d26591b621a0","tid":2257452,"uid":142574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad3fc2d8232704548deffe90f954d2b32a6991ef","tid":2257452,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/Jh2vrwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FJh2vrwq.jpg&h=e0bcee73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國脫